The value at which the security server starts assigning automatically generated
UNIX IDs. Default is value of highest UNIX ID currently used on machine being
configured, incremented by value of \*LUID_GAP\*O.  
There is no requirement that the value of \*LLOW_UID\*O be 
higher than the machine's highest UNIX ID, but if you supply a 
