The increment above highest currently used UID at which security service
starts assigning automatically generated UIDs. The value of this variable is
used with the \*LLOW_UID\*O variable to set the starting point for UIDs 
automatically assigned by the security server. Default is 100. Used in
security server configuration.
T}
